      "date": "2011-05-18 10:27:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/0acec5d8-8139-11e0-b4df-52540025f9af).  Ran 1 tests.  No failures.",
